# QRScanner
QRScanner Lambda function

NodeJS Application build for Lambda function with runtime NodeJS 12.x

Jimp and qrcode-scanner library are used for functionalities

Lambda function is configured with index.handler and main function should be in index.js


Sample Request:
{
  "body": "{\"base64str\": \"\"}"
}

Sample Response:
{
  "statusCode": 201,
  "body": "{\"data\":\"Niranjan from vattakudi\"}",
  "headers": {
    "Access-Control-Allow-Origin": "*"
  }
}
